\newlabel{fig:dpcd_module_8083682}{{3.6}{14}{Co-expression relationship within the dPCD gene module -- example on NAC domain-containing protein 79 (EGI: 8083682) co-expression cluster. Red outline: TF genes; Blue outline: dPCD enzymes. This network is constructed by querying NAC domain-containing protein 79 (EGI: 8083682) with its 7 co-expressed partners (Table~\ref {tab:tf-coexpressed-enzymes})}{figure.caption.16}{}}
